Application Name: Upgrade Your Cereal - Basic Edition
Project Name: UpgradeYourCerealBasic
Package Name: com.jasonhsu.upgradeyourcerealbasic
Minimum Required SDK: Android 2.2
Target SDK: Android 4.2
Compile with: Android 4.2
